descriptionHtml:
This is the very first file I add to Nexus. It's just a preset made thanks to Temptress race mod and a few others applications. Hope
you enjoy. To run this preset without any troubles you have to install the following:

1. Racemenu
2. Temptress Race
3. Eyes of Beauty
4. Apachii SkyHair
5. Brows - High Resolution
6. Seductive Lips HD
7. KJ Tattoos - Overlay Plugins for RaceMenu - KJ Tattoos 4K Models and textures

The armor visible on screenshots is from DreamBurrows Regal Huntsman Armor and the Earrings from [b]Nostromo79[/b] Pierced Ears All in One.

To install it extract and copy the file to your Skyrim -> Data -> SKSE -> Plugins -> CharGen -> Presets folder. Then, run Skyrim and choose Temptress race from race menu,Â  change the sex to female and load the preset.

I think that's all. Hope everything works fine.
